    Enclosing class:
    AnnotatedFieldInjection

    public static class AnnotatedFieldInjection.AnnotatedFieldInjector<T>
extends AbstractFieldInjector<T>
    Injection happens after instantiation, and through fields marked as injection points via an Annotation. The default annotation of com.picocontainer.annotations.@Inject can be overridden.
